<https://data.bp4mc2.org/id/lto/legaltech/fbm/v/1.0> lto:beschrijving <https://data.bp4mc2.org/id/lto/legaltech/fbm/v/1.0/documentatie/90c7f40a-0a07-40de-819a-6b50de1e0652> ;
